The dollar and euro rose in price on Forex to historical highs
24 February 2022, 09:07
Photo: ©
"IZVESTIA" / Pavel Bednyakov
Read ren.tv in
The American currency jumped to almost 90 rubles, the euro rose to 101 rubles, according to Bloomberg data.
Earlier it was reported that the Moscow Exchange suspended trading.
Let us remind you that this morning the President of Russia
made a decision
about the special operation in Donbass.
Aggravation of the situation in Donbass
Since February 17, the situation in the DPR and LPR began to deteriorate. The DPR authorities announced on this day that the situation on the contact line had worsened. On February 18, the head of the republic, Denis Pushilin, said that Ukrainian troops were preparing for an offensive in the Donbass. Because of this, a temporary evacuation to Russia was announced.
February 21, heads of the DPR and LPR
contacted
to Russian President Vladimir Putin with a request to recognize the independence of the republics. On the same day, the head of state signed two decrees recognizing the sovereignty of the LPR and DPR.
Regarding the attitude of the Russian population regarding what is happening in Donbass: VTsIOM
conducted research
and found out that 73% of respondents support the decision to recognize the independence of the DPR and LPR.
On the evening of February 23, the Verkhovna Rada
approved the decree
President of Ukraine Vladimir Zelensky on the introduction of a state of emergency from February 24 throughout the country, except for the Donetsk and Luhansk regions, because a special legal regime has been in effect there since 2014.
